Design Trends Prompt Appender — 45s talk track

This is the Design Trends Prompt Appender — a Figma plugin that turns curated design trends into ready-to-use AI prompts.

Browse ten 2026 aesthetics, each with example imagery and a full prompt library built in. Pick a trend, add an optional theme like Animals or Architecture, and turn on sticker mode if you need a single die-cut or an eighteen-up sheet layout.

One tap copies a Weave-ready prompt to your clipboard — and saves the trend to your selected frame, so the creative direction stays with the file.

No blank prompt box. No guesswork. Just consistent, on-brand generation.

